---
title: Smoky Chicken Caesar Sandwiches with Slaw & Roasted Potato Wedges
description: Blackening Spice and everything nice—that’s what these sandwiches are made of! Caesar dressing, mayo, smoked paprika, and lemon juice turn cabbage into a tangy topper, while chicken is seared with our peppery Blackening Spice. Everything’s stuffed between toasted brioche buns and served with garlicky potato wedges on the side. Feel like these flavors warrant a BBQ? Try grilling the chicken instead for a weeknight meal with a cookout feel.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smoky-chicken-caesar-sandwiches-4c20cd44.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/smoky-chicken-caesar-sandwiches-62e96221eddf590de00e3fa2-ad69c767.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/smoky-chicken-caesar-sandwiches-62e96221eddf590de00e3fa2
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: North America
